Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:57.19,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,4000,4420)\pos(217.133,744.083)}Zhang Fei \NStyled: Yide StyleName·
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't until meeting you that my horizons broadened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Never did I expect our times together to be so short.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is overwhelmed with grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.32,0:01:48.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,5200,5700)\pos(210.923,743.2)}Liú Bèi\N Styled: Xuándé
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorely deprived of the fate to spend more time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will serve the new Lord well, so that you will achieve status and fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am but a man with little talent, yet you regarded me so highly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's unfortunate parting is for my elderly mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:14.40,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,500,7200,7600)\pos(634.923,633.2)}Xú Shù \NStyled, Yuánzhí
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Cao Cao threatens me  —
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,, — I shall never, for the rest of my life, offer a single plan for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After you have gone —
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,, — I shall also hide myself deep within the mountains and woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With my mother in distress, my state of mind is in turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I stayed, I wouldn't be able to improve the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord should find another talented and virtuous man to assist you in achieving your great cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord should not be so discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Among all the able men under the heavens, I am afraid none can compete with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I, a mediocre man, be deserving of such high praise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope all your officers will serve the Lord well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so that your names are recorded in silk and your achievements go down in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My work will remain incomplete, you should not follow after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return, my Lord, and take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I send you off for a 1000 li, farewells are unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Attendants! Attendants! Cut down all those trees over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.24,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(238.997,750.22)}Guān Yǔ\NStyled: Yúncháng
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They are preventing me from seeing Yuanzhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They are hindering my view.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:04.42,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1164.497,744.083)}Zhāng Fēi\NStyled: Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have returned, can it be that you will not go to Xudu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In my turmoil, I forgot a thing of utmost importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There exists this ingenious man —
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,— who resides in Lóngzhōng, which is 20 li from the city of Xiangyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not seek for his assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is reduced to ashes with your departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words are incorrect, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you remain this way then I will make my leave with a heart of stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Never looking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What I said was indeed words of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I naturally know of my lord's heart of benevolence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But uttering such words while your great cause is incomplete —
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,, — will only disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There are numerous talented men above me. I am neither jesting nor being humble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire ought to seek after them for achieving your great cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case —
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,, — I will trouble you to invite him to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This man cannot be recruited with such informalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord must go seek him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If sire is successful —
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,, — it will be no different from the Zhōu gaining Lü Wàng, or the Hàn gaining Zhāng Liáng!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:24.98,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Lü Wàng AKA. Jiāng Zǐyá
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How does this man compare with mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}If you are to compare me with him —
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318} — it is like comparing a frail horse with a qilin, or a jackdaw with a phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}This man compares himself with{\i1} Guǎn Zhòng {\i0} and{\i1} Yuè Yì  —{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:48.96,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Guǎn Zhòng and Yuè Yì are two of the greatest philosopher-statesmen and military- generals of the Spring and Autumn and Warring States period respectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}He has the ability to sew Heaven and Earth together, a genius who looms over all others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I wish to know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}This man is from {\i1}Yángdū{\i0}  of {\i1}Lángyá-commandery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}His name is {\i1}Zhūgě Liàng{\i0}, styled{\i1} Kǒngmíng
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}He lives on a ridge of hills called {\i1}Wolong-Hillock —
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:06.96,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Literally "Sleeping Dragon-Hillock"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318} — which is why he calls himself{\i1} the Sleeping Dragon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}If you have this man's assistance you will have no worries about securing the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}Could he be the one from when people speak of \N{\i1}Sleeping Dragon  {\i0}and{\i1} Fledgling Phoenix?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Fledgling Phoenix is {\i1}Páng Tǒng{\i0}  from Xiāngyáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}That Sleeping Dragon is indeed Zhuge Kongming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}Today I finally know who \NSleeping Dragon and Fledgling Phoenix are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I did not expect them to be right before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}If not for Mister's words, I would remain blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I will take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}With this departure, we are now separated by the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I wonder when we might meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:21.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,In order to weaken Liu Bei's influence and gain the capable man for his own use —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:25.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— Cao Cao schemed to lure Xu Shu into Xudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:31.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,After turning back 10 li to recommend Zhuge Liang to Liu Bei —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:38.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— Xu Shu took a detour to meet Zhuge Liang in Nanyang to tell him of his recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:48.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Having sent Xu Shu away, Liu Bei prepared to visit Zhuge Liang along with Guan Yu and Zhang Fei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.03,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(215.299,540)}Mother of Xu Shu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, please forgive your impious son for arriving late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My son!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you come to Xudu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, I was assisting Lord Liu in Xinye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I saw your handwritten letter to call for me, so I rushed here night and day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did I write a letter to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This...this is not my letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.49,0:11:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How muddled you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After you have roamed the world for so many years —
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,, — I would think your learning had progressed, but you have regressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My son, you are an educated man —
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,, — you know you can only fulfill either filial piety and loyalty, not both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not see that Cao Cao deceives and insults the Dynasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Liu Xuande's compassion stretches across the whole realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he is also a kinsman of \Nthe House of Hàn! You were assisting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You were serving a noble lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, because of a scrap of forged letter—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,— you left the light for darkness! You tarnish your own name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My son —
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I even look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:13:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have brought disgrace upon our family!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there is nothing left for you in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Third brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the gifts have all been prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can now go to Wolong-Hillock to visit Mister Zhuge Kongming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should you trouble yourself? Just send me and Second Brother if you are concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Zhuge Liang is a sagacious prodigy of our time. I must go in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Elder Brother! Third Brother and I will go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can leave the matters here with Zilong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My Lord, there is a gentleman outside. He is wearing a wide belt —
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,— has the shape of a pine and the frame of a crane, and he wishes to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Sir Kongming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the main gate and invite him in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Shuijing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Since leaving you, I have been preoccupied with military affairs and couldn't visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Your arrival today comforts my longing heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard that Yuanzhi is here, so I have come to see him in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi has left for Xudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuanzhi hates Cao Cao the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he go to Xudu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao imprisoned his mother and she wrote a letter for him to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Yuanzhi left for Xudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He was tricked! That was a trap of Cao Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a seat to talk, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have known that his mother is a honorable woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:23.56,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\bord9\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5200,5920)\pos(1216.315,744.083)}Sīmǎ Huī\NStyled: Décāo)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she was imprisoned, she would never write a letter to tell her son to follow Cao Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This letter must have been forged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If Yuanzhi didn't go, his mother would live,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but if he did go, she will definitely die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a woman of high principles with a deep hatred for Cao Cao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But also, she has a fierce personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Having witnessed her son abandon the light for darkness, she must feel ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She will die for honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She lived upholding it, and will die for it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What a muddled man Yuanzhi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What a muddled man he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:37.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,After Xu's mother hanged herself —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:41.14,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— Cao Cao led both his military and civil officials to commemorate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:46.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Xu Shu buried his mother in Nanyuan of Xudu and kept vigil at her tomb —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:51.59,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— As long as the gift was from Cao Cao, Xu Shu would firmly reject them —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:57.29,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— and secretly vowed to never come up with any strategem for Cao Cao —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,— to keep his promise to Liu Bei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he parted, he recommended Zhuge Liang from Nanyang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this man like, sire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If Yuanzhi went, then so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But why should he ask Zhuge Liang to spit blood sweat, and tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}Kongming is a close friend with Cui Zhouping, Shi Guang —
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318} — Meng Gongwei, and Xu Yuanzhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}The talents of these four men surpass many.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Only Kongming is has superior talent and strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}He once joked to the four that —
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318} —they would be governors and prefects if they went into politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}The four then asked where his ambitions lay,\N but he laughed without answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}He regularly compared himself with Guǎn Zhòng and Yuè Yì.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}His talents cannot be measured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Hmph, Mister Shuijing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}Though I am no scholar, I have read\N the {\i1}Spring and Autumn Annals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Guǎn Zhòng and Yuè Yì were two of\N the greatest men of the Eastern Zhōu era.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}Their achievements encompassed the world. For Kongming to compare himself with them —
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)\bord14.318}— isn't that not too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}In my opinion, he not only can compare with these two —
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}— he can also be compared with two other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Oh? Which two?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Jiang Ziya, who kept Zhōu lasting for 800 years —
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}— and Zhang (Liang) Zifang who set up the 400 years of Hàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the general is busy, I should not disturb him and will make my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, to be frank, I was just about visit Wolonggang to seek Mister Kongming with my two brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the Sleeping Dragon has found his lord, he has not been born in the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pity, oh what a pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a true wise hermit, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:21.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}The sky is like a round lid, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:29.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}The earth is like a chessboard, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:40.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Humans are split into black and white chess pieces, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:49.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}They struggle for glory and honour, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:55.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}The victors are naturally at peace, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:21:02.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}While the losers are definitely busy and mediocre, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:08.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}There is a hermit in Nanyang, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:21.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}He sleeps but does not rest enough, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:28.73,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}The sky is like a round lid, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:37.23,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}The earth is like a qi-board, {\i1}oh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:42.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}This ballad sees through the rise and fall of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}I wonder who composed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:53.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318\i1}...They struggle for glory and honour, oh!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:58.25,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}The victors are naturally at peace, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:05.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}While the losers are definitely busy and mediocre, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a song pleasing to the ears from the field with elegant and deep verses —
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,, — and would dare to ask, who is it composed by?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was composed by Mister Wolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.97,0:22:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does Mister Sleeping Dragon reside?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go south along this path and you will reach Wolong-Hillock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There is a hut among the bamboo groves before the h.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.31,0:22:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's where Mister Sleeping Dragon resides.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.98,0:22:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful place!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is knocking at the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pass on that {\i1}Hàn General-of-\Nthe-Left{\i0}, {\i1}Precinct-Marquis of Yicheng{\i0} —
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.01,0:24:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,, — {\i1}Potentate-candidate of Yù-Province{\i0}, \NImperial Uncle Liu Bei, is here to visit Mister Zhuge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.02,0:24:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So wordy, I can't remember that many titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.49,0:25:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then simply tell him that \NLiu Bei has come to seek him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.16,0:25:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher has already left this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.63,0:25:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where has he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.20,0:25:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,His journey is uncertain. I don't know where he has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.17,0:25:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When will he return?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.74,0:25:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That is uncertain, could be three, five, or a dozen days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.42,0:25:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, since he's not here, why not return?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.54,0:25:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait a while more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.36,0:25:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.86,0:25:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The page already said that\N the return date is uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.51,0:25:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go back for now, and later send for someone to find out when he will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.92,0:25:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It would not be late to visit him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.67,0:25:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When your teacher returns, please tell him about Liu Bei's visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.64,0:25:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take these gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take the gifts, but I will remember your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.31,0:26:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That man holds himself well, he must be Sir Wolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.96,0:27:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, are you Sleeping Dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.40,0:27:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kong Ming's friend, {\i1}Cui Zhouping {\i0}of {\i1}Boling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.36,0:27:18.49,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,5000,5420)\pos(1250.633,586.583)}Cuī \NZhōupìng
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.57,0:27:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard of your name, and am honored to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.24,0:27:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we please have a seat, I would like to inquire about some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.34,0:27:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.85,0:27:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.65,0:27:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you wish to see Kongming?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.22,0:27:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is now in turmoil, and warfare is constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.78,0:27:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We have come to visit Mister Sleeping Dragon for a plan to pacify and reform the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.04,0:27:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.04,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318}Eh, though sir seeks to pacify, while with kindness, chaos is but a constant since ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.16,0:28:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318} Untouched by the strength of men.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.90,0:28:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord14.318}If you seek to ask Kongming to take the stage, \Nto restore the Hàn dynasty,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.54,0:28:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318} —I'm afraid it will be a wasted effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.62,0:28:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\bord14.318} General must know that those who follow Heaven lives in harmony, while those who defy it fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.72,0:28:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,997.182)}{\bord14.318}How could men oppose the natural order of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.57,0:28:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words do carry insight —
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.17,0:28:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as a kinsman of the House of Hàn, I should be restoring the Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.48,0:28:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I cast away this Heaven's mandate?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.01,0:28:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.32,0:28:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your aspirations are understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.50,0:28:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am but a mere peasant, and am not enough to discuss such great matters with the emperor's uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.98,0:28:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you have asked, I can only answer impromptu.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.43,0:28:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I receive your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.83,0:28:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder where Sir Kongming has gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.63,0:29:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am also visiting Sir Kongming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.37,0:29:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, shall we go to Xinye together?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.27,0:29:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been a free spirit for long, \NI have no need for making a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.88,0:29:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your intentions, I hope to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.95,0:29:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't see Kongming, instead saw \Nan egghead! What a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were the words of \Na hermit... A hermit indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.17,0:29:50.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}The warrior has yet to create a name for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.27,0:29:55.57,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Alas! For he hasn't met a sagacious lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.92,0:29:58.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}Come! Another cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.41,0:30:06.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}The warrior has yet to create a name for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.51,0:30:12.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Alas! For he hasn't met his sagacious lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.51,0:30:20.51,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}Don't you see, the sage is alone with the wine in a remote valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.51,0:30:31.81,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}With whom can he discuss statesmanship and statecraft?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.50,0:30:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of training troops in the winter —
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.80,0:30:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,— we're trudging here to meet with some braggart!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.98,0:30:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This cold will harm Elder Brother's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.37,0:30:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we return to Xinye?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.98,0:30:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Kongming to know my sincerity. \NIf Third Brother is afraid of the cold, you may return.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.60,0:30:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go ahead with Yunchang.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.41,0:30:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not afraid of death, let alone the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.58,0:31:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want Elder Brother waste his effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.79,0:31:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.30,0:31:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, look! There's an inn there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.30,0:31:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the place for a drink to warm ourselves up!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.67,0:31:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.08,0:31:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Have another!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.60,0:31:34.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}People speak of the history long past;
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.98,0:31:39.98,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}the valiant soaring eagle crowns the military officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.20,0:31:46.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}For my life, I only have aspirations for the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.20,0:31:58.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Who is willing to comment on the heroes now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.90,0:32:00.70,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1002.273)}{\bord14.318}Brilliant! What a brilliant song!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.25,0:32:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be another song by Sir Wolong!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.90,0:32:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Third brother, have some wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.68,0:32:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in, come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.28,0:32:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.86,0:32:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask who among you is Sir Wolong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.53,0:32:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? What are you seeking Mister Sleeping Dragon for?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.44,0:32:51.00,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(325.133,382.038)}Shi \NGuangyuan
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.50,0:32:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Liu Bei and would like to visit Mister Wolong —
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.65,0:32:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,— to ask for methods to cure the world and help the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.94,0:33:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We are all friends of Mister Wolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.45,0:33:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am {\i1}Shi Guangyuan{\i0} from Yingchuan, this is {\i1}Meng Gongwei{\i0} from Runan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.10,0:33:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're nearly frozen, and we still haven't seen Kongming!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.02,0:33:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, let's be on our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.38,0:33:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long heard of your great name, what a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.33,0:33:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have horses here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.57,0:33:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,May I invite you to visit Sleeping Dragons's Retreat for a chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.50,0:33:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We are mere peasants of the mountains and know nothing of state affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.80,0:33:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to be bothered with.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.25,0:33:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir should mount your horse and seek Wolong yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.05,0:33:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead, as you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.58,0:33:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disturb, please continue drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.48,0:33:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What arrogant men, and Elder Brother still wants to treat them with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.32,0:33:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.31,0:33:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, you lower yourself too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.90,0:34:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If we are the kind to forsake strategy and just fight at the command table —
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.67,0:34:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,, — how can we secure the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.72,0:34:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Innkeeper, innkeeper! Bring the wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.85,0:34:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.72,0:34:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.39,0:34:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother  —
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.27,0:35:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,, — I accompany you through hell or high waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.50,0:35:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I only ask you to not suffer this kind of misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.30,0:35:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand your good intentions, my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.97,0:35:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But do both of you know what's in my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.98,0:35:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the help of a sage man, how can the vows that we swore when we became brothers come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.98,0:35:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What great cause is there to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.37,0:35:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of valor, no one can match you two and Zilong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.91,0:35:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, we have suffered continuous defeat all these years —
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.64,0:35:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,— roaming here and there without any firm foothold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.22,0:36:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As Shuijing said, it was because we had no wise men to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.73,0:36:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder brother, say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.33,0:36:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be on our way after this cup of wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.68,0:37:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kongming! Kongming! Are you at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.39,0:37:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear third brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.19,0:37:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.59,0:37:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.56,0:37:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.07,0:37:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your teacher here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.00,0:37:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher is reading in his room, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:12.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}"The phoenix soars high, and won't perch on anything other than a parasol."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.50,0:38:21.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}"The scholar is hidden somewhere and won't follow anyone other than his lord."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.50,0:38:29.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}"While he is content with tilling his fields, how I love my hut."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.50,0:38:39.62,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726.136,1043.182)}{\bord14.318}"For now, he is above the qin and books, waiting for the right time."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.82,0:38:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have longed to meet you, but haven't had the fate to do so earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.72,0:38:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since Teacher Shuijing and Xu Yuanzhi has recommended you many times —
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.00,0:38:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,— we came to visit your retreat, but had to return when you weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.90,0:39:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we have braved the snow and storm, and it is our great fortune to be able to see your noble face.
